  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A new adventure begins!</h2><br>Survive in a new hostile and arid environment, lost in the middle of the dunes. You will have to face sandstorms and high temperatures. Find an oasis, explore wildlife and collect resources.<br><br>Beware of the dangers that await you like the mummies. Try to survive by building yourself a shelter until the helicopter picks you up after 50 days.<br><br>Are you ready to take on this challenge and become the master of your own survival?",
